Mahoning County Bar Association v. Theofilos.

[Cite as Mahoning Cty. Bar Assn. v. Theofilos (1989), 43 Ohio St. 3d 610.]

(No. D.D. 87-12 Submitted April 26, 1989 Decided June 14, 1989.)

On Application for Reinstatement.

*611The application for reinstatement to the practice of law is granted. Gus K. Theofilos is reinstated to the practice of law in the state of Ohio.

(For earlier case, see [1988], 36 Ohio St. 3d 43, 521 N.E. 2d 797.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Re snick, JJ., concur.
